title: Tyranid Assassin
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

[[Lictor]]s treat the [[Deathleaper]] as though it were an [[Independent Character]].

In additon, when fighting in a challenge, [[Deathleaper]]'s melee attacks gain the [[Shred]] special rule, and its opponent(s) must reroll successful saving throws against its attacks.